response.summary: BeispielFirma GmbH invoices Alice Müller for cutlery items (Gabeln, Messer, Löffel). The bill lists quantities (Gabeln 15, Messer 10, Löffel 3), unit prices (10.00 €, 5.00 €, 25.00 €) and line totals (150,00 €, 50,00 €, 75,00 €). Subtotal is 275,00 €, plus 19% VAT of 52,25 €, yielding a total invoice amount of 327,25 €. The document includes invoice date 11.05.2023 and contact details of the supplier.
